body_html: From our page about Corp CLAs: "The Corporate CLA is only signed once per corporation. As part of signing the CLA, they designate a Google Group that identifies who at their company is authorized to contribute to Google projects." -- do you know whether you've been added to the appropriate google group, and is the email used on your commits the one that is in that group?
